    <item>
      <title>律师称梅内德斯妻子隐瞒了罪犯赠送汽车的真相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/menendez-lawyer-says-wife-hid-truth-about-car-given-by-felon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯的律师告诉陪审员，这位政客的妻子没有告诉他如何从一名被定罪的重罪犯那里得到一辆奔驰车，而这名重罪犯在该议员的腐败审判期间作证称，这辆车是贿赂所得。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/menendez-lawyer-says-wife-hid-truth-about-car-given-by-felon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:34:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙将增加对乌克兰的军事援助至2.21亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/portugal-will-increase-military-aid-to-ukraine-to-221-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总理路易斯·蒙特内格罗表示，葡萄牙计划今年将向乌克兰提供的军事援助金额增加至 2.21 亿欧元（2.39 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/portugal-will-increase-military-aid-to-ukraine-to-221-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 17:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，大多数法国人表示投票后国家“无法治理”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/most-french-say-country-is-ungovernable-after-vote-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Elabe 所做的民意调查显示，四分之三的受访者表示，提前举行的立法选举导致法国议会严重分裂，组建稳定政府的路径不明，法国已陷入难以治理的境地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/most-french-say-country-is-ungovernable-after-vote-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:31:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱经济改革面临四大障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/milei-s-plan-for-argentina-economic-overhaul-faces-4-big-hurdles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱伊去年秋天在竞选中警告选民，他将采取的稳定该国持续低迷经济的“休克疗法”将是痛苦的，他的预言成真了。自米莱伊 12 月 10 日上任以来，消费者价格通胀加速：在取消价格管制、货币贬值并开始削减一些抑制运输价格的补贴后，截至 5 月份，价格上涨了 100% 以上，比去年同期上涨了 276%]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/milei-s-plan-for-argentina-economic-overhaul-faces-4-big-hurdles</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚寻求美国提供新爱国者系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/romania-seeks-new-patriot-system-from-us-after-ukraine-donation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚表示，在向邻国乌克兰捐赠了两套爱国者导弹防御系统之一后，该国正在与美国和其他北约伙伴进行谈判，以获得额外的爱国者导弹防御系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/romania-seeks-new-patriot-system-from-us-after-ukraine-donation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佩洛西称坚持参选的拜登必须做出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/pelosi-says-biden-who-insists-he-s-running-must-make-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前众议院议长南希·佩洛西拒绝支持总统乔·拜登寻求连任的意图，而是表示这仍是他的决定——这是民主党对现任总统的年龄和在 11 月击败共和党人唐纳德·特朗普的能力感到不安的最新信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/pelosi-says-biden-who-insists-he-s-running-must-make-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:47:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登支持者和筹款人乔治克鲁尼要求总统放弃竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-10/urgent-actor-george-clooney-a-high-profile-biden-supporter-and-fundraiser-asks-president-to-leave-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他在《纽约时报》的一篇评论文章中写道，他喜欢拜登，但如果他成为候选人，共和党将输掉总统竞选，并失去在国会的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-10/urgent-actor-george-clooney-a-high-profile-biden-supporter-and-fundraiser-asks-president-to-leave-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:23:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙呼吁广泛多数派排除极左翼和极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/macron-says-parties-must-talk-to-build-broad-majority-to-govern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙呼吁代表“共和力量”的政党在政治中心获得广泛多数，此前提前选举导致法国议会分裂，组建稳定政府的前景不明朗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/macron-says-parties-must-talk-to-build-broad-majority-to-govern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:13:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称乌克兰可使用英国导弹袭击俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-ukraine-can-use-uk-missiles-to-strike-inside-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默暗示乌克兰可以使用英国的“风暴影子”导弹袭击俄罗斯境内的军事目标，并证实他将延续英国上届政府在俄乌战争中使用远程武器的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-ukraine-can-use-uk-missiles-to-strike-inside-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
